echecs-moralise_-university-of-chicago-library-ms-392.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/93fea2b2-2b7f-41f8-be5a-6113ed94242a/essay-le-jeu-des-echecs-moralise_-university-of-chicago-library-ms-392.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/93fea2b2-2b7f-41f8-be5a-6113ed94242a/essay-le-jeu-des-echecs-moralise_-university-of-chicago-library-ms-392.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/93fea2b2-2b7f-41f8-be5a-6113ed94242a/essay-le-jeu-des-echecs-moralise_-university-of-chicago-library-ms-392.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/93fea2b2-2b7f-41f8-be5a-6113ed94242a/essay-le-jeu-des-echecs-moralise_-university-of-chicago-library-ms-392.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 3840w" src="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/93fea2b2-2b7f-41f8-be5a-6113ed94242a/essay-le-jeu-des-echecs-moralise_-university-of-chicago-library-ms-392.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto"/></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-1 bLA-dMf"><div class="sc-d56bc236-8 gArifC"><div class="sc-d56bc236-5 uJGVm"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-d56bc236-4 gKlMxC">Save</span></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-3 iOJnhy eIqCxs">essay</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-2 iOJnhy llXHdp">History of ideas</p></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-10 tdBWn">Reimagining balance</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-11 hYbLtW">In the Middle Ages, a new sense of balance fundamentally altered our understanding of nature and society</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-12 iOJnhy dFhhBp">Joel Kaye</p></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-6 kQroYe"></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><footer class="sc-8723d312-0 fVfKHB footer" data-test="footer"><div class="sc-ae266dcd-0 sc-8723d312-1 bwTVbW dRXxEN"><div class="sc-70ed4693-0 bxMjPi"><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/essays" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Essays</a><a href="/ideas" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Ideas</a><a href="/videos" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Videos</a></nav></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/about" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">About</a><a href="/contact" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Contact</a><a href="/support" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Support</a></nav></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 dpJmnC gSiEIv"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 hlaCbq"><a href="/feed.rss" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">RSS Feed</a><a data-ga-select-promotion="aeon_footer_donate" href="/donate" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Donate</a><a href="/community-guidelines" class="sc-3f04373c-0 dbDpAl">Community Guidelines</a></nav></div></div><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-461fb0e3-0 dpJmnC kLFZPU"><p class="sc-461fb0e3-3 jpvQAN">Follow Aeon</p><div class="sc-461fb0e3-1 gLIYMZ"><p class="sc-461fb0e3-2 eUzHhb"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/aeonmag" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Facebook"><svg viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-facebook" aria-hidden="true"><g><path d="M1024,512C1024,229.23,794.77,0,512,0S0,229.23,0,512c0,255.55,187.23,467.37,432,505.78V660H302V512H432V399.2C432,270.88,508.44,200,625.39,200c56,0,114.61,10,114.61,10V336H675.44c-63.6,0-83.44,39.47-83.44,80v96H734L711.3,660H592v357.78C836.77,979.37,1024,767.55,1024,512Z"></path><path d="M711.3,660,734,512H592V416c0-40.49,19.84-80,83.44-80H740V210s-58.59-10-114.61-10C508.44,200,432,270.88,432,399.2V512H302V660H432v357.78a517.58,51